00:20:31,220 --> 00:20:34,139
These memories are very precious to you.

268
00:20:34,140 --> 00:20:36,099
They are worth cherishing.

269
00:20:36,100 --> 00:20:40,459
So for our design plan, not only are we keeping the wall,

270
00:20:40,460 --> 00:20:45,120
but we're also giving it a protective cover to keep it safe forever.

271
00:20:45,780 --> 00:20:49,580
Miss Jiang, we appreciate your thoughtful planning.

272
00:20:49,580 --> 00:20:54,420
However, is a simple glass shield the only element in your design?

273
00:20:54,420 --> 00:20:56,339
We can add on some decorations.

274
00:20:56,340 --> 00:20:59,950
We can turn it into a snow globe with snow,

275
00:20:59,950 --> 00:21:03,200
a castle, and music.

276
00:21:03,200 --> 00:21:06,839
Miss Jiang, it sounds more like an idea.

277
00:21:06,839 --> 00:21:09,280
Do you have a specific design?

278
00:21:09,280 --> 00:21:12,000
Specific design?

279
00:21:12,000 --> 00:21:16,480
Ms. Cheng, allow me to introduce the specifics.

280
00:21:16,480 --> 00:21:21,259
For the design of your art gallery, we are planning to implement advanced AR technology.

281
00:21:21,259 --> 00:21:24,299
It won't be just a glass-covered world.

282
00:21:24,300 --> 00:21:27,019
We can replicate the image of your son

283
00:21:27,020 --> 00:21:28,779
with the materials you provide.

284
00:21:28,780 --> 00:21:32,739
We can recreate the memories left on this wall.

285
00:21:32,740 --> 00:21:36,859
In other words, you will be able to see your memories from the past

286
00:21:36,860 --> 00:21:39,640
any time you want.

287
00:21:39,640 --> 00:21:43,720
 We'll put up a glass screen wall at the front. 

288
00:21:43,720 --> 00:21:46,179
 The lighting effect will create a hologram, 

289
00:21:46,180 --> 00:21:48,360
 creating a surreal presentation. 

290
00:21:48,360 --> 00:21:54,780
♫  I'll follow to the end of the world  ♫

291
00:21:54,780 --> 00:21:57,060
♫  He and she  ♫

292
00:21:57,060 --> 00:22:00,840
♫  Round and round, losing ground  ♫

293
00:22:00,840 --> 00:22:02,800
♫  Wandering Earth  ♫

294
00:22:02,800 --> 00:22:05,880
♫  Fading, wiped out  ♫

295
00:22:05,880 --> 00:22:09,859
No matter what dispute we had before, I must thank you.

296
00:22:09,860 --> 00:22:12,260
You make my dream come true.

297
00:22:12,260 --> 00:22:13,619
Thank you.

298
00:22:13,619 --> 00:22:15,900
Thank you for your trust.

299
00:22:15,900 --> 00:22:18,679
Thank you for sharing your experience with us.

300
00:22:18,679 --> 00:22:20,540
It's an honor.

301
00:22:20,540 --> 00:22:22,780
The honor is mine.

302
00:22:22,780 --> 00:22:25,259
Very well. We should get going.

303
00:22:25,259 --> 00:22:26,379
Thank you.

304
00:22:26,380 --> 00:22:27,980
Have a nice day.

305
00:22:31,940 --> 00:22:33,980
We finally persuaded them.

306
00:22:33,980 --> 00:22:36,979
Boss, thank you.

307
00:22:37,820 --> 00:22:40,180
Don't mention it.

308
00:22:57,140 --> 00:23:00,979
Boss, here's your snow globe.

309
00:23:02,440 --> 00:23:03,819
It's yours now.

310
00:23:03,819 --> 00:23:06,479
You did a good job. Take this as your reward.

311
00:23:06,479 --> 00:23:09,699
But this is too valuable. I can't take this.

312
00:23:09,699 --> 00:23:13,199
It's not that expensive. Just a gift from the hotel.

313
00:23:13,199 --> 00:23:17,659
How fortunate of you. You keep getting gifts.

314
00:23:17,659 --> 00:23:19,120
Pack it up. It's yours now.

315
00:23:19,120 --> 00:23:21,060
Thank you, Boss.

316
00:23:38,940 --> 00:23:40,899
Am I more magnificent than the view here?

317
00:23:40,899 --> 00:23:42,379
The view?

318
00:23:42,380 --> 00:23:45,160
The view is no match for your elegance.

319
00:23:45,900 --> 00:23:48,160
Stop fawning over me.

320
00:23:49,360 --> 00:23:53,500
Boss, are you going to fire me?

321
00:23:54,080 --> 00:23:57,939
You haven't paid the medical bills for your aunt.

322
00:23:57,939 --> 00:24:00,840
I can't possibly let you go so easily.

323
00:24:04,020 --> 00:24:08,299
Boss, you know? There is an issue with you.

324
00:24:09,380 --> 00:24:11,060
What is it?

325
00:24:11,060 --> 00:24:13,740
You're cold on the outside, soft on the inside.

326
00:24:17,120 --> 00:24:19,520
I'm not soft on the inside.

327
00:24:19,520 --> 00:24:21,640
You just can't see it.

328
00:24:29,640 --> 00:24:32,619
Let's go. The sun is about to go away.

329
00:24:32,619 --> 00:24:34,519
The sun is never going away.

330
00:24:34,519 --> 00:24:37,019
You just can't see it sometimes.

331
00:24:37,019 --> 00:24:39,499
Earth's rotation blocks your line of sight

332
00:24:39,499 --> 00:24:41,699
but the sun is always there.

333
00:24:41,699 --> 00:24:43,880
Whether you like it or not,

334
00:24:43,880 --> 00:24:46,760
the sun will rise the next morning.

335
00:24:46,760 --> 00:24:49,280
Don't always look at the negative side.

336
00:24:49,720 --> 00:24:53,359
Just like my parents, they are never gone.

337
00:24:53,359 --> 00:24:56,100
They are always in here.

338
00:24:57,260 --> 00:25:02,900
If you can't change your life, then make the present days happy ones.

339
00:25:06,820 --> 00:25:09,720
Why are you telling me this?

340
00:25:09,720 --> 00:25:12,419
Because I once saw the light in your eyes.

341
00:25:12,419 --> 00:25:15,280
But it didn't last long.

342
00:25:15,280 --> 00:25:19,400
I think you're a man of stories.

343
00:25:19,400 --> 00:25:22,080
I saw the light in your eyes.

344
00:25:22,080 --> 00:25:26,320
It's the kind of happiness that I wish will never disappear.

345
00:25:26,320 --> 00:25:29,220
I don't want you to lose that light.

346
00:25:34,740 --> 00:25:37,900
Did I say too much just now?

347
00:25:38,980 --> 00:25:43,060
Not at all... You're right.

348
00:25:43,060 --> 00:25:45,220
Life is short.

349
00:25:45,220 --> 00:25:47,740
Why not make it a happy one?

350
00:25:58,620 --> 00:26:00,880
The view here is nice.

351
00:26:10,020 --> 00:26:13,160
It looks better a little to the right.

352
00:26:32,740 --> 00:26:34,840
 You must be Mr. Gu. 

353
00:26:37,260 --> 00:26:39,340
 Don't apologize to me. 

354
00:26:40,020 --> 00:26:42,850
 Apologize to my female assistant. 

355
00:26:46,020 --> 00:26:49,820
♫  A scalding wave of heat is coming  ♫

356
00:26:49,820 --> 00:26:51,430
 Boss! 

357
00:27:00,660 --> 00:27:03,460
 Why do I keep thinking of him? 

358
00:27:06,460 --> 00:27:09,779
♫  Two felines sleeping soundly  ♫

359
00:27:09,779 --> 00:27:13,019
 Jiang Xiaoning, you finally got a job. 

360
00:27:13,019 --> 00:27:16,600
 What are you thinking? 

361
00:27:19,200 --> 00:27:21,600
 I'm doomed. 

362
00:27:22,100 --> 00:27:27,120
♫  Diana pink roses  ♫

363
00:27:27,120 --> 00:27:31,800
♫  My heart is wavering like the grass blades  ♫

364
00:27:32,960 --> 00:27:37,420
♫  Time passes by gently  ♫

365
00:27:37,420 --> 00:27:42,540
♫  Our gaze meets unknowingly  ♫

366
00:27:42,540 --> 00:27:47,360
♫  Are you moved  ♫

367
00:27:47,360 --> 00:27:52,080
♫  Open the window and witness the new moon  ♫

368
00:27:52,080 --> 00:27:57,600
♫  Embrace the yearning that comes with a pouring rain  ♫

369
00:27:57,600 --> 00:28:01,200
♫  You said hello as you smiled  ♫

370
00:28:09,900 --> 00:28:15,340
♫  The fog is getting thicker  ♫

371
00:28:15,340 --> 00:28:20,760
♫  The sky has been covered by the rain clouds  ♫

372
00:28:22,040 --> 00:28:25,620
 It looks better a little to the right. 

373
00:28:25,620 --> 00:28:31,000
♫  I forgot what I saw in you  ♫

374
00:28:31,000 --> 00:28:36,040
♫  Diana pink roses  ♫

375
00:28:36,040 --> 00:28:40,820
♫  Slowly withered  ♫

376
00:28:41,840 --> 00:28:46,000
♫  The moment flies like an arrow  ♫

377
00:28:46,000 --> 00:28:48,320
 Send me the photo from earlier. 

378
00:28:48,320 --> 00:28:53,940
♫  The flashbacks and images  ♫

379
00:28:53,940 --> 00:28:58,780
♫  My love is long gone  ♫

380
00:29:00,100 --> 00:29:01,500
   

381
00:29:04,640 --> 00:29:07,219
 I once saw the light in your eyes. 

382
00:29:07,219 --> 00:29:09,139
 But it didn't last long. 

383
00:29:09,139 --> 00:29:12,240
 I don't want you to lose that light. 

384
00:29:18,520 --> 00:29:21,080
 I mean the photo of the afterglow. 

385
00:29:23,940 --> 00:29:26,879
 Sorry, Boss. I made a mistake. 

386
00:29:31,520 --> 00:29:36,240
♫  Where have you been?  ♫

387
00:29:36,940 --> 00:29:42,840
♫  Is it the rain, mist, or the tears  ♫

388
00:29:42,840 --> 00:29:48,740
♫  I want to run away from this summer day  ♫

389
00:29:48,740 --> 00:29:52,179
 Jiang Xiaoning, are you drunk? 

390
00:30:13,920 --> 00:30:16,399
Good morning, Director Gu. The files are on your desk.

391
00:30:16,399 --> 00:30:17,720
Okay.

392
00:30:17,720 --> 00:30:20,580
Who gave you the flowers? They're pretty.

393
00:30:20,580 --> 00:30:22,080
I bought them myself.

394
00:30:22,080 --> 00:30:23,880
You bought them?

395
00:30:23,880 --> 00:30:25,559
What are the flowers for?

396
00:30:25,559 --> 00:30:27,479
Is this for an important client?

397
00:30:27,479 --> 00:30:29,579
If you need more, I can go get some.

398
00:30:29,580 --> 00:30:32,519
No. I bought them for myself.

399
00:30:35,100 --> 00:30:36,860
Is Jiang Xiaoning here?

400
00:30:36,860 --> 00:30:37,879
She is.

401
00:30:37,879 --> 00:30:40,240
Send her to my office.

402
00:30:47,980 --> 00:30:50,779
Cheng Dong, you two will be in charge of this project.

403
00:30:50,779 --> 00:30:53,140
Your focus is...

404
00:31:01,720 --> 00:31:03,799
To whom are those flowers for?

405
00:31:03,799 --> 00:31:05,119
No idea.

406
00:31:05,119 --> 00:31:07,960
I was worried that drinking coffee on an empty stomach might cause a stomachache,

407
00:31:07,960 --> 00:31:09,940
so I brought some snacks.

408
00:31:09,940 --> 00:31:12,219
Xiaoning, how thoughtful of you.

409
00:31:12,219 --> 00:31:14,919
I didn't have time for breakfast. I'm starving.

410
00:31:14,919 --> 00:31:17,479
Dong, give me the meat jerky.

411
00:31:17,479 --> 00:31:19,099
I need to replenish my energy.

412
00:31:19,099 --> 00:31:21,439
Thanks, Xiaoning. You're becoming more attentive.

413
00:31:21,439 --> 00:31:24,560
Of course not, I learned from the best.

414
00:31:24,560 --> 00:31:29,319
Xiaoning, our boss has more trust in you now.

415
00:31:29,319 --> 00:31:32,299
When your career takes off, don't forget me.

416
00:31:32,299 --> 00:31:34,459
I've never thought about something so far away.

417
00:31:34,459 --> 00:31:35,920
No way.

418
00:31:35,920 --> 00:31:39,219
By the way, leave the trivial matters to us.

419
00:31:39,219 --> 00:31:40,299
When you become successful...

420
00:31:40,300 --> 00:31:42,140
Don't forget us.

421
00:31:48,180 --> 00:31:50,839
Sister Manlin, have some coffee.

422
00:31:51,460 --> 00:31:53,660
Director Gu asked for you.

423
00:31:53,660 --> 00:31:55,280
Okay.

424
00:32:03,420 --> 00:32:06,279
Good morning, Boss. You asked for me?

425
00:32:06,279 --> 00:32:08,699
Trim the flowers for me and put them in a vase.

426
00:32:08,700 --> 00:32:10,920
Yes, right away.

427
00:32:11,780 --> 00:32:15,259
Boss, why are you interested in flowers suddenly?

428
00:32:16,240 --> 00:32:18,250
Since I can't change my life,

429
00:32:18,250 --> 00:32:22,130
I must find a way to make my life somewhat happier.

430
00:32:22,139 --> 00:32:24,220
You're making fun of me.

431
00:32:24,220 --> 00:32:27,300
I need you to buy everyone a bouquet of flowers.

432
00:32:28,700 --> 00:32:30,340
Is it a tough task?

433
00:32:30,340 --> 00:32:33,199
No problem. I'll get it done now.

434
00:32:49,780 --> 00:32:51,439
Director Gu bought everyone flowers.

435
00:32:51,439 --> 00:32:54,160
Pick the ones you like.

436
00:32:54,160 --> 00:32:56,140
I'm taking this.

437
00:32:57,000 --> 00:32:58,739
Come on, pick a flower.

438
00:32:58,739 --> 00:33:00,020
 Director Gu really bought us flowers? 

439
00:33:00,020 --> 00:33:01,299
 Is this really happening? 

440
00:33:01,300 --> 00:33:02,179
 Pick a flower. 

441
00:33:02,180 --> 00:33:03,240
 Pick yours now. 

442
00:33:03,240 --> 00:33:04,220
 I want this. 

443
00:33:04,220 --> 00:33:06,379
What's wrong with Boss?

444
00:33:06,380 --> 00:33:07,620
How should I know?

445
00:33:07,620 --> 00:33:09,619
Why is he giving everyone flowers all of a sudden?

446
00:33:09,619 --> 00:33:11,960
Is he in love?

447
00:33:11,960 --> 00:33:13,219
Jiang Xiaoning?

448
00:33:13,220 --> 00:33:15,960
Yes, Jiang Xiaoning.

449
00:33:15,960 --> 00:33:19,139
Nothing is impossible.

450
00:33:19,140 --> 00:33:22,620
Did you finish your work and have nothing to do?

451
00:33:22,620 --> 00:33:24,820
Take it.

452
00:33:29,340 --> 00:33:31,900
Sister Manlin, pick a flower.

453
00:33:41,600 --> 00:33:44,639
 Hello? Director Gu, hello. How may I help you? 

454
00:33:44,639 --> 00:33:46,379
Order some plants for me.

455
00:33:46,380 --> 00:33:47,679
Okay, no problem.

456
00:33:47,679 --> 00:33:49,959
What plants do you want?

457
00:33:49,959 --> 00:33:52,879
 You may ask the florist we used to work with. 

458
00:33:52,879 --> 00:33:54,339
 Ask for his opinion. 

459
00:33:54,340 --> 00:33:57,539
I want my room to be more lively.

460
00:33:57,539 --> 00:33:58,920
 Okay, consider it done. 

461
00:33:58,920 --> 00:34:01,059
 Should I send them to the office? 

462
00:34:01,060 --> 00:34:03,819
Yes. I'll need some for my home, too.

463
00:34:03,819 --> 00:34:05,699
 Okay. You can count on me. 

464
00:34:05,699 --> 00:34:07,500
 Director Gu, bye. 

465
00:34:20,710 --> 00:34:21,739
Hello?

466
00:34:21,740 --> 00:34:25,159
 Gu! Your data seems promising lately. 

467
00:34:25,180 --> 00:34:28,400
I want to know if you're feeling any changes.

468
00:34:28,400 --> 00:34:30,759
Nothing special in particular.

469
00:34:30,759 --> 00:34:33,189
Perhaps it's because I'm not as busy lately.

470
00:34:33,189 --> 00:34:34,609
There is less pressure.

471
00:34:34,610 --> 00:34:37,859
I've told you not to work too hard.

472
00:34:37,860 --> 00:34:40,220
It helps a lot.

473
00:34:40,220 --> 00:34:45,610
Other than work, have you experienced anything memorable?

474
00:34:45,610 --> 00:34:48,440
Nothing special.

475
00:34:48,440 --> 00:34:50,800
Maybe...

476
00:34:50,800 --> 00:34:52,920
I feel a little happier lately.

477
00:34:53,660 --> 00:34:57,659
 Technically, happiness will increase your blood flow, 

478
00:34:57,660 --> 00:35:03,440
which would increase the need for oxygen and the load on your heart.

479
00:35:03,440 --> 00:35:05,340
But this is odd.

480
00:35:06,160 --> 00:35:09,759
However, happiness brings positive results.

481
00:35:09,759 --> 00:35:12,620
Continue being happy.

482
00:35:13,860 --> 00:35:15,500
Okay.

483
00:35:25,040 --> 00:35:27,080
 Charging. 

484
00:35:35,130 --> 00:35:36,330
 Director Gu. 

485
00:35:36,350 --> 00:35:37,950
 Come in. 

486
00:35:39,190 --> 00:35:41,870
There are some issues at the resort.

487
00:35:41,870 --> 00:35:43,110
What's wrong?

488
00:35:43,110 --> 00:35:44,949
It's nothing major.

489
00:35:44,949 --> 00:35:49,149
We made adjustments to the plans, but it involves partial relocation.

490
00:35:49,149 --> 00:35:51,529
The progress will be delayed.

491
00:35:51,529 --> 00:35:52,429
Which means...

492
00:35:52,430 --> 00:35:54,970
Judging by the pace,

493
00:35:54,970 --> 00:35:57,769
we won't make it in time for the Jin An Award nomination.

494
00:35:57,769 --> 00:36:00,290
We'll have to wait for another two years.

495
00:36:01,610 --> 00:36:05,049
 Waiting for another year might not be a setback. 

496
00:36:05,049 --> 00:36:07,510
 But it must not be later than that. 

497
00:36:10,110 --> 00:36:15,049
It's rare to see architects who are so obsessed with one award like you.

498
00:36:15,850 --> 00:36:18,630
Everyone's life is a different story.

499
00:36:19,490 --> 00:36:22,309
We don't have to be so focused on winning the award.

500
00:36:22,310 --> 00:36:24,410
Why not leave it in fate's hand?

501
00:36:25,490 --> 00:36:27,770
I've been waiting to win this award.

502
00:36:27,770 --> 00:36:31,810
Consider it my finish line.

503
00:36:31,810 --> 00:36:35,429
You are still too young to be thinking about the finish line.

504
00:36:35,430 --> 00:36:38,350
Are you not going to live after winning this award?

505
00:36:38,350 --> 00:36:41,330
This one is all I will ever need.

506
00:36:41,330 --> 00:36:42,770
Very well.

507
00:36:42,770 --> 00:36:46,950
However, I've always admired your persistence.

508
00:36:49,290 --> 00:36:53,650
By the way, what's with the sudden interest in plants and flowers?

509
00:36:55,870 --> 00:36:56,829
I don't know either.

510
00:36:56,829 --> 00:37:01,930
Maybe I'm hoping to bring some light to the darkness in my life.

511
00:37:03,450 --> 00:37:05,450
As long as it makes you happy.

512
00:37:13,770 --> 00:37:17,309
 However, happiness brings positive results. 

513
00:37:17,309 --> 00:37:19,990
 Continue being happy. 

514
00:37:38,030 --> 00:37:40,330
The resort project is over for the time being.

515
00:37:40,330 --> 00:37:42,189
Thank you for your hard work.

516
00:37:42,189 --> 00:37:47,830
Tomorrow, all of you will have a two-day team-building event.

517
00:37:47,830 --> 00:37:50,150
Thank you, Boss!

518
00:37:50,150 --> 00:37:52,290
As for the destination, that's up to you.

519
00:37:52,290 --> 00:37:53,769
Okay! Thank you, Boss!

520
00:37:53,769 --> 00:37:55,889
My goodness, he was smiling!

521
00:37:55,889 --> 00:37:57,709
What is going on? Is this really happening?

522
00:37:57,709 --> 00:38:00,029
Is he in love?

523
00:38:00,029 --> 00:38:03,469
Jia Jia, your lipstick is smudged.

524
00:38:03,469 --> 00:38:04,629
Check it out.

525
00:38:04,629 --> 00:38:05,969
Jiang Xiaoning.

526
00:38:05,969 --> 00:38:07,769
- Sister Manlin. 
 - I don't think you'll be able to join us.

527
00:38:07,769 --> 00:38:09,349
You haven't finished your work.

528
00:38:09,349 --> 00:38:10,749
What work?

529
00:38:10,749 --> 00:38:12,929
The presentation for our gallery project.

530
00:38:12,929 --> 00:38:16,969
Not to mention the project statement assigned to you is really urgent.

531
00:38:16,969 --> 00:38:19,870
Okay. No problem.

532
00:38:19,870 --> 00:38:21,790
Xiaoning.

533
00:38:24,390 --> 00:38:27,839
Can't you just finish the work before you come back from the trip?

534
00:38:27,839 --> 00:38:30,310
Is that all right?

535
00:38:30,310 --> 00:38:33,029
Wang Kai, I said no and you dare say yes?

536
00:38:33,029 --> 00:38:36,269
Are you standing against me or are you defending Jiang Xiaoning?

537
00:38:36,269 --> 00:38:39,790
Jiang Xiaoning, can you finish it or not?

538
00:38:39,790 --> 00:38:41,650
I can do it.

539
00:38:47,010 --> 00:38:48,470
Thanks, Brother Kai.

540
00:38:48,470 --> 00:38:49,269
Don't mention it.

541
00:38:49,270 --> 00:38:50,509
It's no big deal.

542
00:38:50,869 --> 00:38:53,630
I can't stand her autocratic manner.

543
00:38:53,630 --> 00:38:55,529
This is my job. Don't worry.

544
00:38:55,529 --> 00:38:58,229
Okay. Keep it on.

545
00:39:11,070 --> 00:39:14,070
Brother Xu, why do you insist that we talk in person?

546
00:39:14,070 --> 00:39:16,269
You just got back from your business trip, you should get some rest.

547
00:39:16,270 --> 00:39:17,709
I brought some souvenirs.

548
00:39:17,710 --> 00:39:19,269
Give them to Grandma and Aunty.

549
00:39:19,270 --> 00:39:20,349
Thank you, Brother Xu.

550
00:39:20,350 --> 00:39:23,090
By the way, one more thing.

551
00:39:25,430 --> 00:39:27,470
What is this?

552
00:39:27,470 --> 00:39:29,550
A small present.

553
00:39:31,960 --> 00:39:34,159
I'll take the souvenirs, but I can't accept this.

554
00:39:34,159 --> 00:39:37,439
Xiaoning, I would be upset if you turned me down.

555
00:39:37,439 --> 00:39:39,059
I'll be mad if you give this to me.

556
00:39:39,060 --> 00:39:41,699
Don't worry. It's cheap. It's not expensive.

557
00:39:41,699 --> 00:39:43,480
 - Let me drive you home. 
 - You're not as nice as you were. 

558
00:39:43,480 --> 00:39:45,601
 I'll help you put it on. 

559
00:39:55,060 --> 00:39:56,630
It's done.

560
00:39:57,380 --> 00:39:58,619
It looks good on you.

561
00:39:58,620 --> 00:40:00,660
Thank you, Brother Xu.

562
00:40:03,020 --> 00:40:05,999
I left something in the office. You can go back first.

563
00:40:09,340 --> 00:40:11,980
- How is it? 
 - Look, you're pretty with it.

564
00:40:16,140 --> 00:40:17,979
 Where have you been lately? 

565
00:40:17,979 --> 00:40:20,500
 You disappeared without a word. 

566
00:40:20,500 --> 00:40:23,539
 Yan Yan, I miss you. 

567
00:40:34,620 --> 00:40:36,660
Love-struck again?

568
00:40:41,840 --> 00:40:44,899
What? Why are you drinking on your own?

569
00:40:44,899 --> 00:40:47,100
You haven't contacted me in a while.

570
00:40:47,100 --> 00:40:48,980
I'm busy.

571
00:40:50,280 --> 00:40:52,180
Busy with what?

572
00:40:52,180 --> 00:40:54,260
I'm busy spending time with my girlfriend.

573
00:40:56,180 --> 00:40:57,940
You have a girlfriend?

574
00:40:57,940 --> 00:41:00,160
Who's the lucky girl?

575
00:41:01,400 --> 00:41:03,699
My perfect lady. Fate brought her to me.

576
00:41:03,699 --> 00:41:08,219
My true love and my buster. I'll spend the rest of my life with her.

577
00:41:08,880 --> 00:41:11,460
You're crazy.

578
00:41:11,460 --> 00:41:13,020
Bye.

579
00:41:18,599 --> 00:41:20,320
One more, please.

580
00:41:34,160 --> 00:41:36,140
 Are you asleep? 

581
00:41:40,540 --> 00:41:43,899
 I'm still awake. I'm thinking about what food I should prepare for you. 

582
00:41:43,899 --> 00:41:46,840
 The food there might not fit your appetite. 

583
00:41:51,400 --> 00:41:52,559
 Hello, Boss? 

584
00:41:52,560 --> 00:41:54,960
Am I that picky with food?

585
00:41:54,960 --> 00:41:57,279
You're not picky, but I am.

586
00:41:57,279 --> 00:42:01,020
As your assistant, it's my duty to make you like me.

587
00:42:01,020 --> 00:42:03,560
I already like you.

588
00:42:07,240 --> 00:42:16,820


