00:42:21,580 --> 00:42:23,659
♫  Destiny is a little annoying  ♫

590
00:42:23,659 --> 00:42:26,600
♫  Takes those I care about  ♫

591
00:42:26,600 --> 00:42:30,340
♫  Away from me  ♫

592
