♫  If memory is bright  ♫

593
00:42:32,199 --> 00:42:35,220
♫  It would hold up a lamp in my heart  ♫

594
00:42:35,220 --> 00:42:39,520
♫  And light up the night  ♫

595
00:42:58,160 --> 00:43:00,199
♫  Sunshine alternates with moonlight  ♫

596
00:43:00,199 --> 00:43:03,279
♫  Returning to life in time  ♫

597
00:43:03,279 --> 00:43:06,820
♫  Gift me with a dream  ♫

598
00:43:06,820 --> 00:43:11,490
♫  A dream with you in it  ♫

599
00:43:35,740 --> 00:43:40,199
♫  The one who caught me off guard  ♫

600
00:43:40,199 --> 00:43:45,240
♫  Steps foot into my life...  ♫

601
00:43:48,840 --> 00:43:53,100
♫  It's you...  ♫

602
00:43:53,100 --> 00:43:57,400
♫  If it weren't for parting  ♫

603
00:43:57,400 --> 00:44:02,600
♫  How can we meet again?  ♫

604
00:44:05,700 --> 00:44:09,980
♫  It's you...  ♫

605
00:44:11,180 --> 00:44:13,219
♫  Exchanging sunshine for moonlight  ♫

606
00:44:13,219 --> 00:44:16,299
♫  Exchanging fortune for the past  ♫

607
00:44:16,299 --> 00:44:20,960
♫  Exchanging my heartbeat for you  ♫

